### Features ###

Recipe generation
Recipe storage

Create recipes from external sources (links, images, etc.)

AI-powered stock management
- Take picture of refrigerator, cupboards, etc.
- AI identifies items and quantities
- Updates stock levels automatically

###Family member preferences###
- In a family each member should have individual preferences

###Add Telegram access###
- Allow users to interact with the app via Telegram bot
- Users can send messages to the bot to get recipe suggestions, check stock levels, etc.
- Users can also upload photos of their fridge, cupboards, etc. to the bot to update stock levels
- Users can also rate meals and upload photos of their meals to the bot
- Users can also create recipes from external sources (links, images, etc.) via the bot